Class FileModifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • FileModifier

  • public class FileModifier
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is here in order to communicate with the database and upload new additions for dynamic backing to the database. THis communicates with both the reports and student text files for minimization of database errors.
    Author:
    Aryan Kaul
